        <abstract> 
<p>CD regrets he used "creation" in <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi> when he meant "appeared".</p>  
<p>An Oken-like article in "Owenian style" in <hi rend="italic">Athenæum</hi>.</p> 
            <p>Tropical plants continue to be troublesome.</p>
